[I] Dolphin is a KDE base package

[T] Dolphin is KDE's file manager that lets you navigate and browse the
[T] contents of your hard drives, USB sticks, SD cards, and more. Creating,
[T] moving, or deleting files and folders is simple and fast.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/dolphin/

